### 💬 CHAT HISTORY API TEST

### Bước 1: Authenticate agent để lấy JWT token
POST http://localhost:5003/api/auth/agent-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "agentId": "agent1",
    "agentName": "Agent Smith"
}

### Bước 2: Get group messages (cần JWT token từ bước 1)
GET http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/group-messages?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

### Bước 3: Get private messages with another agent
GET http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/private-messages/agent2?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

### Bước 4: Get all my messages
GET http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/my-messages?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

### Bước 5: Mark messages as read
POST http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/mark-read/agent2
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

### Bước 6: Get unread message count
GET http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

### Bước 7: Get online agents from database
GET http://localhost:5003/api/chathistory/online-agents
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1}}

